# Telegram notifications for the Product / Engineer agents.
#
# SETUP: copy this file to ".agents/.env" (which is gitignored) and fill in real
# values. Never put real credentials in this template or in the *-agent-prompt.md
# files — those are committed to the repo.
#
#   cp .agents/.env.example .agents/.env
#
# - TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN: create a bot via @BotFather and paste the token it returns.
# - TELEGRAM_CHAT_ID:   message your bot, then read result[].message.chat.id from
#                       https://api.telegram.org/bot<TOKEN>/getUpdates
# See .agents/README.md for the full walkthrough.
#
# In CI, do NOT use this file — inject the same two variables as repository secrets.

TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN=
TELEGRAM_CHAT_ID=
